Class GraphCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.GraphCalculator

  • public class GraphCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    A object show a window that asks user to choose a country and specific period of year. After that, it calculates and shows the total to the user. If the user presses the Enter, it will show the graph of the selected information.
